{"tid":2176284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭轟專家抹黑 何栢良暫別商台《晴朗》訪問 寄語平心靜氣用科學原則應對疫境","createTime":"2020-08-27T04:06:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T04:53:12.000Z","uid":36494,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4579ef7ab174680ca620dfb6a6aae07e02132d57","tid":2176284,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T04:06:23.000Z","msg":"多名醫學專家早前表示個人不會參與全民檢測後，特首林鄭月娥就不點名批評「所謂專家、醫生和一些人」抹黑計劃，阻止市民檢測，是出於政治計算，抹黑中央。過去大半年在商台節目分享防疫意見，並曾表明不參與計劃的港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良，昨（26日）透過短訊向商台表示，將暫停每天在商台的訪問環節，呼籲「市民大眾要平心靜氣，用科學原則去應對，疫境自強」；並寄語商台「繼續為市民講真話」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《晴朗》主持今早就在節目中讀出何栢良的短訊：「近日工作及家務比較忙，所以每天十分鐘的何栢良環節要同大家暫別，感謝商台年初至今畀機會我，同聽眾分享疫情資訊，自己亦獲益良多。今天（即昨天）是商台61歲台慶生日，祝願商台業務蒸蒸日上，百尺竿頭，更進一步，繼續為市民講真話，面對疫境，市民大眾要平心靜氣，用科學原則去應對，疫境自強。」<br />\n主持並表示，昨曾向何栢良了解，「明白有啲嘢大家唔使講出口」，唯有尊重其決定，強調何栢良從來沒有表示有任何壓力，或說過任何人的不是。不過，主持相信是特首「出咗聲」，而且在現時政治氣氛下，令專家們承受壓力，很難暢所欲言給予意見，「因為一啲政治立場唔係咁啱話你，仿佛將專業、疫情問題擺埋一邊。」主持人認為，當失去專家在防疫工作上的資訊，受苦的就是廣大市民。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/CE7RRLVHEZHJ5BGRLPWNC2BSSI/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2FCE7RRLVHEZHJ5BGRLPWNC2BSSI%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk1NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=df6568f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2FCE7RRLVHEZHJ5BGRLPWNC2BSSI%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=bc70241c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/CE7RRLVHEZHJ5BGRLPWNC2BSSI/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"b08c8899058b26a9b3cd96f95996ba64205123f2","tid":2176284,"uid":36494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T04:07:16.000Z","msg":"主持並表示，昨曾向何栢良了解，「明白有啲嘢大家唔使講出口」，唯有尊重其決定，強調何栢良從來沒有表示有任何壓力，或說過任何人的不是。"},{"pid":"21d7da630de9b749765dba39ad5b9291ac79363d","tid":2176284,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T04:07:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3ebb0bf9b363f2d25db4beb0333ccae3c88a7c40","tid":2176284,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T04:07:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2d67a5ed6acd1d4b9ce104158aa79ff6af96dbfa","tid":2176284,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T04:08:44.000Z","msg":"林門鄭氏迫害教授"},{"pid":"b9ba0bc0447744fd7cac36567fcf130a61b41b37","tid":2176284,"uid":24335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T04:09:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c618d5e199bcc07281d08bfbd997d7367753b251","tid":2176284,"uid":113183,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T04:11:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qR8mhTk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqR8mhTk.jpg&h=a2621707&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ea49564aa3b26e9154c6f4b5f04d35bfd18872c","tid":2176284,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T04:11:53.000Z","msg":"聯署支持封殺微信同TikTok<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fwe-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk1NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=1684e066\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok</a><br />\n<br />\n所羅門都叫大家簽呀"},{"pid":"c3719e54d8a647a7f4769f2163b377927799c7a7","tid":2176284,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T04:11:57.000Z","msg":"祝商台早日仆街就真<img src=\"/as